metadata.name: Sultan
metadata.description:
The reign of the new and first female ruler SULTAN, who has sworn to take revenge on the exploitation and massacre of the people, will begin in the Mard Kingdom with a patriarchal society and a fire that has not come down from the skies for centuries in the Land of the Sun.


In this land, people reign on the high hills of the earth, fairies in the sky, devils in the underworld, and various beings in as yet unknown places.

2599 x 3000
